Best editing app ever! I love this, very impressed! It's the best editing 
app I have found/used, and goes over my expectations, very good. Almost 
everything is good, but for the cutting - it's okay that it fills in other 
spaces that was not meant to be filled when you tap for the red to show up 
...Full ReviewBest editing app ever! I love this, very impressed! It's the best editing 
app I have found/used, and goes over my expectations, very good. Almost 
everything is good, but for the cutting - it's okay that it fills in other 
spaces that was not meant to be filled when you tap for the red to show up 
just because you can draw the red, but the drawing has this problem too. 
When you DO draw with the red on the object/person, it fills in spaces 
around the object or person which is kinda annoying. It would aslo be good 
to have an eraser in cutting. Please take my advice on this and update the 
app fixing/adding these things. Other than the two problems in cutting, 
great work. (By the way, these two problems are the only reason I have a 4 
star rating, you have an extra star waiting to be added!)

One of my top editing apps. The only complaint I have is that sometimes the 
removal tool just cuts and pastes another area of the photo into the area I 
want to remove. At other times, it completely removes the area I've painted 
over. Great little app! :)
